strings.Value: "You fight well! Almost as good as Guy Shaseur De Lombair, a hero I've read about. But you lack his style, his dignity. Could you make an epic pose once you have dispatched your wicked opponent? I think that would go a long way to help our group's fame!"
"How about I do the killing, and you do the singing and dreaming? And save the speeches for Tristian, I have no interest in your books."
